 3, 'grey', 'DE', 'ISBN 978-3-86780-304-8',
 'AUTHOR-TITLE-ONLY', 'VERIFIED-2', 'https://eph-psychiatrie.de/',
 '[session_2026-07-19-non-english-research-recovery-batch4] FRESH RESEARCH, not notes-extraction (this slug''s search_languages notes are PRE-REMEDIATION stubs -- see slug-language-tracking-matrix.md). WebFetch non-functional this session. Verified via the companion web portal (eph-psychiatrie.de) structure, an Amazon listing (ISBN), and a secondary "Kurzinfo EPH" document, independently corroborating publisher/funder/year/ISBN. Could not directly read book text -- specific room-dimension/numeric detail is not independently confirmed beyond the topic list in notes below.',
 'Fresh-research recovery per research-handoff-non-english.md, extended to a PRE-REMEDIATION-stub slug (mental-health-built-environment, DE) -- see slug-language-tracking-matrix.md for the substrate-quality distinction from the notes-extraction slugs.',
 'Federally-funded evidence-based planning handbook devoted specifically to psychiatric-facility architecture: wet rooms/bathrooms, doors, windows/façade, building technical services, orientation/wayfinding, staff base and acute-care areas, general design/fittings -- oriented around suicide-prevention design, accessibility, security, and therapeutic environmental design.',
 strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ','now'), 'session_2026-07-19-non-english-research-recovery-batch4', strftime('%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ','now'), 'session_2026-07-19-non-english-research-recovery-batch4'),

